name: RxSwiftUIKit
description: RxSwiftUIKit is an extension of [SwiftUIKit](https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/SwiftUIKit). Combine with [RxSwift](https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/RxSwift) and [Carbon](https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/Carbon), tt gives us the ability to build the tableView or collectionView using the declarative way.
